<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    .container {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .driver-info {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .info-label {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #475569;
    }
    .tracking-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #2563eb;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Delivery Driver Assigned</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>
      
      <p>Good news! A driver has been assigned to your order #{{orderId}}.</p>
      
      <div class="driver-info">
        <p><span class="info-label">Driver Name:</span> {{driverName}}</p>
        <p><span class="info-label">Vehicle:</span> {{vehicleType}} - {{vehiclePlate}}</p>
        <p><span class="info-label">Estimated Delivery:</span> {{estimatedDelivery}}</p>
        {{#if additionalNotes}}
        <p><span class="info-label">Notes:</span> {{additionalNotes}}</p>
        {{/if}}
      </div>
      
      <p>You can track your delivery in real-time using the link below:</p>
      <a href="{{trackingUrl}}" class="tracking-button">Track Delivery</a>
      
      <p>If you need to contact your driver or have any questions, our customer support team is here to help.</p>
      
      <p>Contact Support: {{supportPhone}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you for choosing Vorex Delivery</p>
      <small>This is an automated message, please do not reply.</small>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 